    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;m with you on the &#8220;brunch&#8221; issue.  Besides appreciating sweets, coffee, fruit, bread, butter, jams, cakes, croissants, milk and yogurt in the morning, I find that I help myself to too many things when brunch time rolls around&#8230;</></>Being Italian, we often eat eggs for a light dinner, and I will store this delicious- looking recipe away for that meal!  </></>I love your blog and read often, especially now that I have an impending wedding to read about!  I got married under two years ago so the anticipation and excitement that went along with it is still fresh in my mind.  Good luck with the planning and best wishes!</p>
    </div>

